name: Element_firstElementChildTest
description: Unit tests for the firstElementChild method of the Element class.

test_cases.name: testFirstElementChildWithElement
test_cases.description: Tests the firstElementChild method when an Element child is present.

test_cases.name: testFirstElementChildWithNonElement
test_cases.description: Tests the firstElementChild method when a non-Element child (TextNode) is present.

test_cases.name: testFirstElementChildWithMixedChildren
test_cases.description: Tests the firstElementChild method when both Element and non-Element children are present.

test_cases.name: testFirstElementChildWithNoChildren
test_cases.description: Tests the firstElementChild method when no children are present.
